         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1/12/83 ¶  ¶ With the last mail, dear Mr Holtze, I was asked by Prof. Caspary, the monographer of the Nymphaeaceae, to send him more Australian material. ¶  He would like the flowers and ripe fruits o...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">83.12.01</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Maurice Holtze</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">GRG 19/391, Public Library Museum and Art Gallery, State Records of South Australia, Adelaide.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">1/12/83.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit lezter Post, geehrter Herr Holtze, bat mich der Monograph der <name key="Nymphaeaceae">Nymphaeaceae</name>, prof. Caspary, ihm noch mehr australisches Material zu senden. Er wünscht von unseren 2 oder 3 Arten die Blumen u. reifen Früchte der Länge nach aufgeschnitten zu haben, damit solche selbst bei schnellen Trocknen nicht vermodern. Würden Sie auch uns hierbei Ihre gütige Hülfe gewähren?</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Stets der Ihre</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Haben Sie bereits <name key="Arachis%20hypogaea">Arachis hypogaea</name>? Ich könnte sonst Ihnen frische Samen senden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1/12/83</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With the last mail, dear Mr Holtze, I was asked by Prof. Caspary, the monographer of the <name key="Nymphaeaceae">Nymphaeaceae</name>, to send him more Australian material.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letter not found; see Caspary (1878).</p>
               </note> He would like the flowers and ripe fruits of our 2 or 3 species, cut open lengthwise for them to dry quickly and not to rot. Would you also give us your kind assistance in this matter?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Always yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Do you already have <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Arachis%20hypogaea">Arachis hypogaea</name>
               </seg>?<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">In the 1891 edition of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Select extra-tropical plants</seg> (B91.13.10), M listed for the first time under <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Arachis%20hypogaea">Arachis hypogaea</name>
                     </seg> (Peanut): 'Mr Holtze harvested at Port Darwin 27 cwt. from an acre, the product being saleable at £20 per ton there.'</p>
               </note> If not, I could send you fresh seeds.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Arachis%20hypogaea">Arachis hypogaea</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Nymphaeaceae">Nymphaeaceae</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
